creator: SansaVision
descriptionHtml:
Create beautiful artwork using the power of AI! Enter a text prompt, pick an art style and watch Art Ai, your personal AI Artist/Painter turn your idea into an AI-powered painting in seconds.


So how does Art Ai work? 🖌🖌🖌
Type in whatever you want to create! -- “Kanye west riding a unicorn”, “Pikachu holding a magical crystal ball”, “1800th century rainbow forest” or anything else you can imagine are just a few of the billions of potential paintings that could be made. Let your creativity be the light that guides you.


Pick an art style! -- Whether you’re looking for a vibrant colorful painting or something darker and more dystopian, Art Ai has you covered with an array of selected styles.

Generate your painting! -- Watch Art Ai use the power of AI to transform your idea and art style into a beautiful painting right before your eyes in seconds.

Art Ai is expanding art to the masses. You don’t need a paint brush, pencil, or any art supplies to make beautiful artwork, all you need is an idea. Take a back seat and let Art Ai be the paintbrush to your artwork.

Share your art to your friends and family and save your artwork to your profile so that you can view it for later, it’s that simple!

This application is a Beta version and is under development.
Updates will be done regularly during the development phase.
If any issues are experienced, please contact our customer service.

Art Ai (Text to image) is a new way of turning your text into unique images. Imagine you could tell a painter to paint you anything you could imagine. Now imagine how much that would cost you. This app does the same thing for free. Let this app be your personal A.I. artist and paint you anything you could imagine. The app also allows you to enhance images. You could use these images as wallpapers, avatars or anything you'd like. We are actively working on developing it and making the A.I. part smarter and better.

Done are the days where you have to stress and confuse yourself into bringing your dreams and ideas into reality. Sketching on Photoshop, GIMP or any other photo editor can be a very tedious process. If you want to get a cool and funny or interesting avatar, wallpaper or image really fast based on an idea you have just type the idea as precisely as possible and get 16 visualizations, or images, back. Share these imagaes to Telegram, WhatsApp, Facebook, Instagram or Snapchat. The images are produced relatively fast. Text to image is an interesting concept and will always improve. This is just the beginning, produced images will be more and more clearer and precise.

Art Ai, previously known as Text to Image, is created by the same creators of Disney Face, Clone:ar and Face Restore. We always listen to feedback and impement it as fast as possible.

Thank you for reading, if you have any questions or feedback and want to contact us, our email is support@sansavision.com

Welcome to Art Ai, an app where you can create unique, beautiful and amazing Ai generated art. Art Ai offers image editing (inpainting), image variation, image expansion (outpainting), morphing, face animation, 3d effects, background removal and image enlargement (ie. upscaling/super-resolution).

Generate your painting! Watch Art Ai use the power of AI to transform your idea and art style into a beautiful painting right before your eyes in seconds.
You don’t need a paint brush, pencil, or any art supplies to make beautiful artwork, all you need is an idea. Take a back seat and let Art Ai be the paintbrush to your artwork.

This art app also introduces a brand new concept called "painters". The concept of painters is simple, it allows you to essentially choose the type of painter you want to emulate and create art through the lens of that painter. Painters are specially trained A.I. models which are trained on a specific art style, making it easy for you to create unique art in your desired art style. The app is very fast and can be used to create AI avatars, memes and NFTs. You can transform your children's drawings into beautiful artwork. Alternatively, you can also transform your own art into something new and spectacular. Art Ai offer allows you to swiftly control four simple configurations, creativity (how creative the AI should be), mix (how well the AI-editing should blend), variation (how much variation you want from the original image) and a list of things to avoid. The list of things to avoid is extremely useful when guiding the AI to generate what you want. For example, let's say your art is blurry and you want to deblur it and enhance it, you can add "blurry" to your things to avoid list and this will instruct the Ai to magically create sharp and enhanced art. In addition to that, when writing prompts, we also offer something called "attention", where you can direct the attention of the Ai to a specific word, term or sentence. You can think of this app as your personal Photoshop expert that you can guide however you like to do whatever amazing artwork you like. The created and generated art can easily be saved to your device or shared to multiple different apps such as Facebook, WhatsApp, Telegram, Google drive, IM messenger, Viber, Instagram and many more social media apps.

Generating images from text, ie. text to image, is extremely simple and easy. Just select any of our pre-made and curated styles or create a custom style. Once an image style is selected, you can type in whatever you want the Ai to generate, for example "An astronaut riding a horse in space" and voila, you've just created a masterpiece, a one out of one, unique and excellent piece of art. Following the same steps but using painters you can generate drastically different results with completely different aesthetics in regards to the selected painter. This will further personalize your art and make the art even more unique and exclusive. Art Ai also allows for images to be generated in different aspect ratios (ie. orientations). You can generate portrait (vertical), landscape (horizontal) and perfectly square images. The number of images generated can range from one to four and you, the user, decide how many. When generating two or four images, Art Ai will automatically create a grid collage for you. The grid collage is adaptive and adapts to whatever orientation you decide.

Using the image variation mode you can essentially turn your art into anything. However, through communicating with our users we've learned that many Art Ai users use this mode to turn themselves into characters in the style of anime characters like Disney Pixar, One Piece, Metal Gear Soldier, Robots, futuristic sci-fi cyberpunk art, vibrant colorful painting, something darker and more dystopian, dieselpunk art, vaporwave, neon and digital art and much more. So this mode is perfect for anyone wanting to avatarify themsleves and create beautiful Ai Art.

descriptionHtml:
Experience the ultimate creative freedom with Art Ai - Ai Art Generator, a powerful application designed to transform your photos and text into mesmerising works of art. Inspired by popular AI tools like Jasper art, Mid journey, Stable Diffusion, and Wombo Dream, our application harnesses the potential of artificial intelligence to create captivating art pieces. Turn words into art, explore a variety of art styles, and generate unique masterpieces showcasing your imagination and creativity.

Unleash your artistic potential with Art Ai - Ai Art Generator, a cutting-edge application that caters to both professionals and amateurs. Delve into the wonders of AI-generated art as you explore styles like Cubism, Dali, and Deviant. Utilise our advanced artificial intelligence technology to effortlessly create amazing artwork that will leave you in awe.

✨ Key Features:

► Advanced AI Art Generator:
Generate stunning art in just a few taps using our AI art generator, inspired by leading tools like Wombo Dream. Transform your photos into vivid, sharp, and visually appealing works of art, perfect for sharing on social media or displaying in your home.

► Comprehensive Art Styles Library:
Discover a vast range of art styles, including imaginary, Cubist, Dali, and many more. Experiment with unique combinations and explore different art styles to find the perfect aesthetic for your masterpiece.

► Custom AI Avatars:
Design professional-quality AI avatars for use on platforms like LinkedIn, Tinder, and Facebook. Stand out from the crowd with custom AI-generated photos that showcase your style and personality.

► Powerful Photo Editing Tools:
Enhance your images with advanced photo editing features, such as brightness, contrast, and other adjustments. Our application also includes powerful image enhancement tools that add clarity, depth, and stunning visual effects to your photos.

► Face Animation and Enhancement:
Bring your photos to life with our face animation and face enhancement features. Create mesmerising animated effects that showcase your personality and style, perfect for sharing with friends and family.

► Unique Filters and Effects:
Choose from an extensive collection of filters and effects to create truly unique and stunning images. Experiment with different combinations to achieve the perfect look for your artwork.

► Artwork Wonders:
Experience the wonders of AI-generated art as you create masterpieces in various styles like Cubism, Dali, and Deviant. Unleash your creativity and explore the endless possibilities of artificial intelligence-powered art.

► Diffusion and Combo:
Mix and match different art styles using our diffusion and combo features, allowing you to create one-of-a-kind pieces that reflect your artistic vision.

► AI Artists Community:
Join a community of AI artists and share your creations with like-minded individuals. Discover new art styles, get inspired, and learn from fellow artists as you embark on your journey through the world of AI-generated art.

With plenty of rich features and functionalities, Art Ai - Ai Art Generator is the ultimate application for creating professional-quality art and photos. Experience the magic of AI-generated art and unleash your creativity today by downloading our application. Begin your artistic journey and explore the fascinating world of AI-generated art with Art Ai - Ai Art Generator. Download now and start creating masterpieces!

If you have any questions, need assistance, or would like to share your feedback, please feel free to reach out to our dedicated support team at support@sansavision.com. We are committed to providing you with the best possible experience and are always eager to hear from our users. Your input helps us continually improve our application and provide you with exceptional service. Don't hesitate to contact us – we're here to help and ensure that your artistic journey with Art Ai - Ai Art Generator is nothing short of extraordinary!
